<p>The above <a href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=21140" data-linktype="external">assessment</a> is based on the types of systems affected by the vulnerability, their typical deployment patterns, and the effect that exploiting the vulnerability would have on them. While the OWC are installed in conjunction with server products, best practices recommends against the usage patterns, visiting untrusted web sites and reading HTML email, required to exploit these vulnerabilities on servers.</p>
<p><strong>Vulnerability identifiers:</strong></p>
<ul>
